'''Kurtz''' is a [[franco]] living in [[Franco Village]] on the [[Island of the Francos]], in [[Mr. Kurtz's house|a house]] where he made sure no sunlight can come in. His flowers are the proof of that. According to the sign outside his house, Mr. Kurtz is a retired colonel. He currently works as a scientist.

Kurtz is one of the many Francos searching for their [[Francos Fragment|fragment]] which is lost on the island. He spends his time in his house concocting a potion which he believes will lead him directly to the fragments location. Unfortunately, he lost the vial which contained the potion.

